      "date": "2013-07-29 06:58:38.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/48f4bd0c-f81c-11e2-a8b3-52540035b04c).  Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
