        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Jinshan Xiong",
          "email": "jinshan.xiong@intel.com",
          "date": "2013-07-29 18:11:27.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-3647 hsm: do not verify data_version for restore",
        "message": "LU-3647 hsm: do not verify data_version for restore\n\nIn ll_ioc_copy_end(), it used to verify data_version for restore.\nThis is not required because layout lock was already held by\nrestore request on the MDT side so that we can't verify whether\nlayout is stale. Therefore ll_data_version() uses stale layout to\ncall getattr to OFD which causes ENOENT, then this error code will\nbe transferred to MDT to result in restore failure.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I8595d244399d84962d2af151b2d78459b10c56b4\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
